---
---
<section id="tecnologia" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-cosmos-dark border-y border-gray-800">
  <!-- Watermark Map and Backlight Glows -->
  <div class="absolute right-[-10%] top-[10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-contain bg-no-repeat opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none select-none -z-10 mix-blend-screen" style="background-image: url('/wheel.png');"></div>
  <div class="absolute left-1/4 top-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-cosmos-blue/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-1/4 bottom-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-gold-deep/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Cabecera Limpia -->
    <div class="animate-on-scroll text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-gold-deep text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] sm:tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-glow">INGENIERÍA DE SOFTWARE DE ALTO NIVEL</h2>
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-normal font-heading mb-6 text-white tracking-wide">Ecosistemas Digitales <span class="italic text-gold-bright">Resilientes y Robustos</span></h3>
      <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gold-deep/50 mx-auto mb-8 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(136,192,208,0.8)]"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Construimos arquitecturas enterprise diseñadas para escalar de forma inquebrantable, integrando la estabilidad de una base sólida con la flexibilidad de la innovación continua.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Diseño de Ecosistema: Explicación Intuitiva + Diagrama Visual -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Columna Izquierda: Explicaciones sin tecnicismos complejos -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-4">
        
        <!-- Tarjeta 1: Alta Disponibilidad -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll glass-card p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 transition-all hover:border-gold-deep/30 flex items-start gap-4 group">
          <!-- Icono SVG Servidor/Redundancia -->
          <div class="p-3 bg-gold-deep/10 rounded-lg text-gold-bright transition-colors group-hover:bg-gold-deep/20 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" />
              <rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" />
              <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6" stroke-width="2" />
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18" stroke-width="2" />
              <path d="M17 6h1" />
              <path d="M17 18h1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors">Alta Disponibilidad <span class="italic text-gold-deep text-xs font-normal block sm:inline sm:ml-2">(Tu web nunca se detiene)</span></h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
              Tu plataforma permanece activa el 99.99% del tiempo. Si un servidor falla, otro toma su lugar automáticamente al instante para que nunca pierdas clientes ni ventas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 2: Ciberseguridad -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll glass-card p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 transition-all hover:border-cosmos-blue/30 flex items-start gap-4 group">
          <!-- Icono SVG Escudo -->
          <div class="p-3 bg-cosmos-blue/15 rounded-lg text-cosmos-blue transition-colors group-hover:bg-cosmos-blue/25 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-cosmos-blue transition-colors">Fortaleza Digital <span class="italic text-gold-deep text-xs font-normal block sm:inline sm:ml-2">(Protección Blindada)</span></h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
              Resguardamos tus datos y los de tus clientes con cifrado avanzado y verificación continua. La información confidencial de tu empresa estará 100% protegida contra accesos no autorizados.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 3: SaaS Inteligente -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll glass-card p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 transition-all hover:border-gold-deep/30 flex items-start gap-4 group">
          <!-- Icono SVG Cerebro / IA -->
          <div class="p-3 bg-gold-deep/10 rounded-lg text-gold-bright transition-colors group-hover:bg-gold-deep/20 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-gold-bright transition-colors">SaaS e Inteligencia <span class="italic text-gold-deep text-xs font-normal block sm:inline sm:ml-2">(Automatización a Medida)</span></h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
              Creamos software a la medida que automatiza tus procesos diarios y conecta Inteligencia Artificial para ayudarte a tomar mejores decisiones comerciales analizando tus datos en tiempo real.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarjeta 4: Infraestructura Nube -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll glass-card p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 transition-all hover:border-cosmos-blue/30 flex items-start gap-4 group">
          <!-- Icono SVG Nube -->
          <div class="p-3 bg-cosmos-blue/15 rounded-lg text-cosmos-blue transition-colors group-hover:bg-cosmos-blue/25 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-base font-heading font-semibold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-cosmos-blue transition-colors">Ecosistema Cloud <span class="italic text-gold-deep text-xs font-normal block sm:inline sm:ml-2">(Crecimiento sin Límites)</span></h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs sm:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">
              Tu plataforma corre sobre servidores en la nube de alta velocidad (AWS y GCP) que se adaptan y expanden automáticamente a medida que tu negocio recibe más visitas y clientes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Columna Derecha: Imagen del Diagrama Visual -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 animate-on-scroll relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-cosmos-blue/20 to-gold-deep/20 rounded-2xl blur-lg opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="glass-card p-2 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 relative z-10 hover:border-cosmos-blue/30 transition-all duration-500">
          <img 
            src="/digital_ecosystem_diagram.png" 
            alt="Esquema Visual de Ecosistema Digital Pegaso System" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-2xl filter brightness-90 hover:brightness-100 transition-all duration-500"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
